These large cats require a regular supply of drinking  
water, although otherwise they do not care for this  
element.  

Lions compete with and sometimes prey on the other  
carnivores found on the savannah. They will  
sometimes kill and eat leopards and cheetahs. Lions  
and hyenas have a particular dislike for one another.  
Adult male lions will go out of their way to kill  
hyenas. 
 
